  <div class="script-box">
    <span class="direction">[Solo on camera — back at the pond, end of day, slightly tired, genuine]</span>
    <p>"Alright… so that was a lot."</p>
    <p><em>(Small laugh)</em><br>"I think what surprised me most today was just… how much is actually going on in a pond that you never see. Like, you look at it from the outside and it just looks like water. But underneath that — there's a whole system working to keep everything alive."</p>
    <p>"And I get it now. I really do. If you're a pond owner and you've been putting off maintenance… please don't."</p>
    <p><em>(Beat)</em><br>"Your fish will thank you."</p>
    <p>"Next time on Fishy Jobs… we're not maintaining a pond. We're building one. From scratch."</p>
    <p><em>(Smile)</em><br>"See you then."</p>
